subSubSection.paragraph:
Geographical distribution. Bermudas , Gulf of Mexico, Antilles, Panama , Puerto Rico , and Brazil (
Pawson et al . 2010
). In Brazil from Paraíba to Bahia in Northeast coast. The species was recorded in depths down to 70 m (
Hendler et al. 1995
). The specimens analyzed were found between 10–15 m depth.
